Going Gone is out now! When I received the vocal-demo in September 2022 I immediately catched a vibe and had the vision to combine bass elements from my songs clock ticker and shades on for the first drop and combine it with piano house vibes as in my song “Alright” for the second one. I’m super proud of how this song embodies a lot of different aspects of my sound. After testing out 3-4 versions I sent it to @confessionlabel and I’m super happy they again trust in my music ❤️ hope u guys enjoy this tune and I’m happy about any support 🫶 #ghouse #techhouse #piano #newmusic
